        &lt;p&gt;This page shows simple examples of the three building blocks of Goka to get you up and running in no time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check out the &lt;code&gt;Guide&lt;/code&gt; for an in-depth introduction to all components or dive into more complex &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/lovoo/goka/tree/master/examples&#34;&gt;examples&lt;/a&gt; in the repository.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;adding-data-to-kafka&#34;&gt;Adding data to Kafka&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s start by pushing some data to a Kafka-Topic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;
